12/27/2005: Version 2.0
  General:
    * YML-based configuration file
  Indexer:
    * No longer regenerates the swish-e.conf
    * "-S prog" based dynamic index content generation
    * uses SWISH::Filter system instead of configured converters
    * Indexes web history URLs
    * Use Snowball stemming by default
  Server:
    * Now uses POE::Component::Server::HTTPServer instead of 
	       POE::Component::Server::HTTP (oh, boy!)
    * Logs accesses
    * More flexible IP restrictions
    * Username/Password authentication

12/12/2004: Version 1.0
